# AreaIQ API Testing Suite
# This file contains HTTP requests for testing AreaIQ API endpoints
# Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar HTTP client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
# For production testing, change to:
# @baseUrl = https://www.onegoodarea.com

# Test user credentials (create test accounts first)
@testEmail = test@example.com
@testPassword = testpassword123
@adminEmail = admin@example.com

# API Keys (generate these in the app first)
@apiKeyFree = aiq_test_free_key
@apiKeyDeveloper = aiq_test_developer_key
@apiKeyBusiness = aiq_test_business_key

# Session tokens (will be set after authentication)
@sessionToken =

### ============================================================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### ============================================================================
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS (NextAuth)
### ============================================================================

### Sign In with Credentials
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signin/credentials
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}",
  "redirect": false
}

### Sign Up
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Forgot Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}"
}

### Reset Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "reset-token-here",
  "password": "newsecurepassword123"
}

### Resend Verification Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resend-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}"
}

### ============================================================================
### REPORT GENERATION (Authenticated Users)
### ============================================================================

### Generate Report - Moving Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "SW1A 1AA",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### Generate Report - Business Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "Shoreditch, London",
  "intent": "business"
}

### Generate Report - Investing Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "M1 1AE",
  "intent": "investing"
}

### Generate Report - Research Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "Manchester City Centre",
  "intent": "research"
}

### Generate Report - Invalid Location
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "Invalid Location 123",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### Generate Report - Rate Limited (expect 429)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "B1 1AA",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### ============================================================================
### API V1 REPORTS (API Key Authentication)
### ============================================================================

### Generate Report via API - Free Plan (expect 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKeyFree}}

{
  "area": "SW1A 1AA",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### Generate Report via API - Developer Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKeyDeveloper}}

{
  "area": "SW1A 1AA",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### Generate Report via API - Business Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKeyBusiness}}

{
  "area": "Shoreditch, London",
  "intent": "business"
}

### Generate Report via API - Invalid API Key (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid-api-key

{
  "area": "SW1A 1AA",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### Generate Report via API - No API Key (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "area": "SW1A 1AA",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### ============================================================================
### SETTINGS ENDPOINTS
### ============================================================================

### Get User Settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### Update Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/settings/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "currentPassword": "{{testPassword}}",
  "newPassword": "newsecurepassword123"
}

### Get Subscription Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/settings/subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### Cancel Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/settings/cancel-subscription
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "reason": "Testing cancellation flow"
}

### Delete Account
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/settings/account
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "confirmation": "DELETE_MY_ACCOUNT"
}

### ============================================================================
### API KEYS MANAGEMENT
### ============================================================================

### Generate API Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/keys
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "name": "Test API Key"
}

### List API Keys
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/keys
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### Revoke API Key
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/keys
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "keyId": "api-key-id-here"
}

### ============================================================================
### USAGE TRACKING
### ============================================================================

### Get Usage Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/usage
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### ============================================================================
### WATCHLIST MANAGEMENT
### ============================================================================

### Add to Watchlist
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/watchlist
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "postcode": "SW1A 1AA",
  "label": "Test Area",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### Get Watchlist
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### Remove from Watchlist
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/watchlist
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "postcode": "SW1A 1AA"
}

### ============================================================================
### STRIPE WEBHOOKS (for testing payment flows)
### ============================================================================

### Stripe Webhook - Subscription Created
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stripe/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
Stripe-Signature: t=1234567890,v1=test-signature

{
  "id": "evt_test_webhook",
  "object": "event",
  "api_version": "2020-08-27",
  "created": 1234567890,
  "data": {
    "object": {
      "id": "sub_test_subscription",
      "object": "subscription",
      "status": "active",
      "customer": "cus_test_customer",
      "items": {
        "data": [{
          "price": {
            "id": "price_developer_monthly"
          }
        }]
      }
    }
  },
  "livemode": false,
  "pending_webhooks": 1,
  "request": {
    "id": "req_test_request",
    "idempotency_key": null
  },
  "type": "customer.subscription.created"
}

### ============================================================================
### ADMIN ENDPOINTS (Admin Only)
### ============================================================================

### Get Admin Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### Get Traffic Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/traffic
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### ============================================================================
### WIDGET ENDPOINTS
### ============================================================================

### Get Widget Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/widget?area=SW1A%201AA&intent=moving

### ============================================================================
### TRACK EVENT (Analytics)
### ============================================================================

### Track User Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/track
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "event": "report_generated",
  "properties": {
    "area": "SW1A 1AA",
    "intent": "moving",
    "score": 75
  }
}

### ============================================================================
### ERROR TESTING
### ============================================================================

### Invalid Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/invalid-endpoint

### Method Not Allowed
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/report

### Unauthorized Access
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/settings
# No authorization header

### ============================================================================
### LOAD TESTING SCENARIOS
### ============================================================================

### Rapid Report Generation (for rate limit testing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "SW1A 1AA",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### Multiple API Calls (for rate limit testing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKeyDeveloper}}

{
  "area": "M1 1AE",
  "intent": "business"
}

### ============================================================================
### EDGE CASES
### ============================================================================

### Report with Special Characters
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "St. John's Wood, London",
  "intent": "moving"
}

### Report with Very Long Area Name
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "This is a very long area name that might cause issues with database field lengths or validation rules in the system",
  "intent": "research"
}

### Report with Empty Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

{
  "area": "SW1A 1AA",
  "intent": ""
}

### ============================================================================
### CORS TESTING
### ============================================================================

### Preflight CORS Request
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/report
Origin: https://example.com
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Content-Type,Authorization</content>
<parameter name="filePath">/home/narister/projetos/AreaIQ-/api-tests.http